data.description: Motivated Sellers! Hunting Enthusiasts This is the Property For You! Bring Your Animals/Mini Farm! Amazing Views from Your Wrap-Around Porch! Custom Built Log Home on almost 30 acres. Primary Suite Downstairs with New Soaking Tub and Walk-In Shower. Large Eat-In Kitchen with New Appliances Including Touch-Top Stove, Double Oven, and Dishwasher. Amazing Floor to Ceiling Brick Fireplace. HVAC System and Water Heater are New. Bedrooms Upstairs Each Have a Private Balcony. Washer, Dryer, Refrigerator, TVs, and Wood Burning Stove to Remain. Property has a Pasture, Two Horse Run-Ins, 60X40 Garden, and a Shed. No Business Creek Runs Through the Back of the Property. Explore Caves, Waterfall, Mountain Views, Abundant Wildlife, and Trails. Property Backs Up to Catoosa Wildlife Mngtmnt - Never Have Development Behind You! 1600 sq ft Unfinished Walk-Out Basement (not included in Sq. Ft.). Additional Structure Has Been Framed and Waiting For Your Finishing Touches!
